                      <p class="text-muted">Every decision we make is centered
                        around improving our customers' experience.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                  <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                      <i
